{
  "text": "It would seem to me that from the configuration of this male entity encouraged forward it looks to the left and the right foot is pointed to the left. That this card would indicate that you must be in a defensive position with respect to the left-hand path, with no need to concern yourself about protection with respect to the right hand path. Comment on that? Again, this is not the suggestion we wish to offer by constructing this image. However, the perception cannot be said to be incorrect.",
